Henry Roberto Cuellar (born September 19, 1955) is a Democratic politician from Laredo, Texas, who represents his state''s 28th Congressional district (map) in the United States House of Representatives. Cuellar''s district extends from the Rio Grande to the suburbs of San Antonio, including Guadalupe County. Seller Inventory # 9786131636639
